description: '''Head Wound City''' is an American [[hardcore punk]] [[Supergroup (music)|supergroup]] consisting of [[Jordan Blilie]] and [[Cody Votolato]] both of [[The Blood Brothers (band)|The Blood Brothers]], [[Nick Zinner]] of the [[Yeah Yeah Yeahs]], and [[Justin Pearson (musician)|Justin Pearson]] and [[Gabe Serbian]], both of [[The Locust]].
